                <XMTok font="italic" role="UNKNOWN">I</XMTok>
                <XMTok meaning="24.5" role="NUMBER">24.5</XMTok>
              </XMApp>
            </XMath>
          </Math> mag. Both of the early-types and late-types
in the both fields show a slight dip at <Math mode="inline" tex="I\sim 23.8" text="I similar-to 23.8" xml:id="S3.SS2.p4.m4">
            <XMath>
              <XMApp>
                <XMTok meaning="similar-to" name="sim" role="RELOP">∼</XMTok>
