  <section refnum="4" xml:id="S4">
    <title><tag close=" ">4</tag>PHOTOMETRIC REDSHIFTS</title>
    <para xml:id="S4.p1">
      <p>We have determined photometrically the redshifts of about 340 galaxies
with <Math mode="inline" tex="I&lt;26" text="I less 26" xml:id="S4.p1.m1">
          <XMath>
            <XMApp>
              <XMTok meaning="less-than" role="RELOP">&lt;</XMTok>
              <XMTok font="italic" role="UNKNOWN">I</XMTok>
              <XMTok meaning="26" role="NUMBER">26</XMTok>
            </XMApp>
          </XMath>
        </Math> mag in the HDFS and of about 400 galaxies in the HDFN
using the empirical training set method described in Wang et al. (1998, 1999).
Wang et al. presented the calibration for the empirical training set
based on 82 galaxies with measured spectroscopic redshifts <Math mode="inline" tex="0.1&lt;z&lt;3.5" text="0.1 less z less 3.5" xml:id="S4.p1.m2">
          <XMath>
            <XMApp>
              <XMTok meaning="multirelation"/>
